{"tid":1948301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遇到仆街業主想唔交租","createTime":"2020-03-29T02:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T18:44:14.000Z","uid":262075,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f06a37fe8dbfb40c99e0caadb2be99d7fdaf26","tid":1948301,"uid":262075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:22:13.000Z","msg":"個仆街業主間屋有事乜都唔理<br />\n<br />\n第1日住沖涼廁所道門閂埋左開唔返，困左我成個鍾<br />\n<br />\n毛巾電話都係廳，好彩有較剪剪得開<br />\n<br />\n差啲要開窗叫救命搵人報警<br />\n<br />\n之後廁所道門漏水又唔整返攪到扇親，雙膝跪地成分鍾，成個膝頭跌到黑q曬 <br />\n<br />\n電費又借啲2想收貴<br />\n<br />\n又成日聞到屎味，周圍又嘈，長期訓唔到<br />\n<br />\n到宜家肺炎咁差攪到收入少左<br />\n<br />\n同佢講減租一蚊都唔減，間屋有問題乜都唔理<br />\n<br />\n仲有半年有多先走得  宜家直情唔L想交租<br />\n<br />\n應唔應該咁做好?"},{"pid":"7ddb3d0bfd25b3ac46fc2fa5e4ed5a99ae50a10e","tid":1948301,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:23:05.000Z","msg":"諗下點解你咁低賤買唔起樓要做租租啦🙈"},{"pid":"e597d8ab28a43205a48035b6fb7cadb7ec45dca9","tid":1948301,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:23:44.000Z","msg":"日日租樓日日賺🙈"},{"pid":"235fb23540a21b0d1379ec712fd2277940162ae9","tid":1948301,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:24:11.000Z","msg":"廢柴幫大業主供樓🙈"},{"pid":"5816b1f9e7f373207027720899d8972aa768bfc0","tid":1948301,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:24:55.000Z","msg":"現代奴隸每月返工養大業主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba593290c5b5efbb02a8c930b7df9a3c621f6a5","tid":1948301,"uid":93277,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:26:12.000Z","msg":"唔洗交啦，佢搵得執達吏出黎收屋都要等一年半載先搞到，佢仲要驚你整爛佢間屋，靠惡就得"},{"pid":"082405f06fe9cc537b8b087214e2555ae69abede","tid":1948301,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你隻乞衣租租你又玩得出咩花樣？<br />\n<br />\n隨時可以趕你走<br />\n<b